      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "chn": "呵呵呵……",
      "jap": "フフフ…",
      "eng": "Meh heh heh...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "chn": "怎么啦，今天真是听话啊……呵呵呵……",
      "jap": "どうした、やけに素直ではないか…フフフ…",
      "eng": "Oh why can't they all be this easy?...Meh heh heh",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "chn": "#0第2次说话",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:2回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-2nd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "chn": "哼……果然够难缠！……",
      "jap": "フン…やはりじゃじゃ馬よの…！",
      "eng": "Hmph! Hmm! We've got a wild one here!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "chn": "乖乖听老子摆布！……还不乖乖听老子摆布！……",
      "jap": "言うことを聞け…！言うことを聞かぬか…！",
      "eng": "Shape up! Shape up, I say!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "chn": "#0第3次说话",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:3回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-3rd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "chn": "哦……很好……这个好……",
      "jap": "おお…いいぞ…これはいい…",
      "eng": "Oh-hoh hoh hoh! That's it, yes, that's the way!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "chn": "火啊火……旺旺地烧吧……呵呵呵……",
      "jap": "火よ…火よ…さかるがよい…フフフ…",
      "eng": "Dear flame...how brightly you burn! Meh heh heh...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "chn": "#0第4次说话",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:4回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-4th time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "chn": "差不多该加点余烬了……",
      "jap": "そろそろ、種火を足さねばか…",
      "eng": "I ought to fetch a new ember...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "chn": "火啊……火啊……",
      "jap": "火よ…火よ…",
      "eng": "Flame, dear flame...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "chn": "#0持有将熄余烬时说话",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:5回目・鈍い種火を持っている",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" After acquiring the Dull Ember",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "chn": "火的味道……小子身上有火的味道。",
      "jap": "火のにおい…貴様は火のにおいがする",
      "eng": "Flame flame...I smell flame upon you.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "chn": "老子叫麦道夫\r\n有火万事足的普通铁匠。",
      "jap": "儂はマックダフ\r\n火の他には何もいらぬただの鍛冶屋よ",
      "eng": "I'm McDuff the blacksmith;\r\nall I want is a little flame.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "chn": "来，把余烬给我。",
      "jap": "さあ、その種火を寄こせ",
      "eng": "So, hand that ember to me.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "chn": "快拿来，\r\n小子。",
      "jap": "早くしろ\r\n貴様",
      "eng": "Right now,\r\nyou imbecile.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "chn": "#0将熄余烬要交付出去吗？选择「否」",
